0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"從前從前 有個人愛你好久<br />\n但偏偏風漸漸把距離吹得好遠"},{"pid":"78ae319f3ba4a75f37ec59e99165b62cd8e07f19","tid":993014,"uid":141994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"等多排<br />\n分咗手大把歌你聽"},{"pid":"18987b91f984036c253adb9176970efe6ba863db","tid":993014,"uid":95031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:04:30.000Z","msg":"原地轉"},{"pid":"a2c771b41df9ff055a3ce23636ea628f15e107b1","tid":993014,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"太難重新開站 倒流時光一次<br />\n讓你是我未說的心事 無下次<br />\n為何在遇見之時未在意<br />\n明日怎可再任性一次"},{"pid":"b0b003fb2819539358782b5b1d7cb3a7a3f49257","tid":993014,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:07:23.000Z","msg":"如想見卻不可以再遇<br />\n分開不等於思念中斷<br />\n曾傷我   最深的<br />\n卻令我懂得   怎去愛   下一個<br />\n若有一天    我終於    放底你    我亦感激你   <br />\n愛是   越痛我越難恨你<br />\n最後   我笑著   懷念你"},{"pid":"e3409c18840ec2658fe91572425b9927394b5d56","tid":993014,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"如果傑克沒有沉入大西洋底<br />\n如果英雄沒有捨身炸掉彗星<br />\n如果每個故事都像賀歲電影<br />\n愛就不會如此刻骨銘心<br />\n<br />\n最美電影不必有最好的結局<br />\n最美愛情只需要永恆的曾經<br />\n如果心碎能成全你雋永劇情<br />\n為你犧牲是我的榮幸"},{"pid":"6f9672d596e686e4661f945f7dc4d7797c75cdb7","tid":993014,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"和你道謝 和你道別 如告別後 難再會面 <br />\n無拖與欠 仍想致歉 如果過去 妨礙半天<br />\n<br />\n和你道謝 和你道別 難免日後 難忘你的臉 <br />\n留低再見 如不再遇見 都感激為更好留低了伏線<br />\n<br />\n當哭泣證實過相愛 哪有快樂純屬意外 <br />\n如遺下憾事一堆 方可使你悲哀 就讓我這秒 離開"},{"pid":"cbd4d0cd159ae07ced779e872d8830d86493817a","tid":993014,"uid":3325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mzB1VGEGcSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmzB1VGEGcSU&d=SNcgiO0Jsq9L6NEwCudGKf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=929f7495\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mzB1VGEGcSU</a>"},{"pid":"d1ddc2ec33fcffdc18e7517304759bdf87b6fd77","tid":993014,"uid":11989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"想你說討厭我 我也可改變我 不過你偏偏說永遠感激我<br />\n不到你不到我 你也很想吻我 假裝親暱更生疏<br />\n<br />\n要追究要補救 但望著你內疚 要痛恨找不到矛頭<br />\n不管愛不透愛不夠 妒忌亦要虛構<br />\n想痛哭都找不到淚流<br />\n<br />\n無目的分手痛在無可厚非 沒有他搶走你比失手更悲<br />\n誠實的分手沒法延續遊戲 還謝謝你 放低演技<br />\n<br />\n情感之死有墓碑欠日期 沒道理"},{"pid":"eb1173dda9ce25e8ecef6883847699454fe3aa68","tid":993014,"uid":42174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:12:21.000Z","msg":"熱帶雨林<br />\n<br />\n相戀的關係猶像熱帶雨林<br />\n逐分鐘消失4.8哩"},{"pid":"b79cac845978b278a7b7f68fe2c150e440691b4c","tid":993014,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:37:15.000Z","msg":"周杰倫 藉口"},{"pid":"0341ea29b19cec95d925d30632c33814ece4ac57","tid":993014,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"終止戀愛"},{"pid":"520333637564c541d76c8e5039ce49bd515d31ae","tid":993014,"uid":139967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"你在何地 - 張國榮"},{"pid":"c685db5404b4153acf318345c6a8d0b341269092","tid":993014,"uid":71959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T02:36:21.000Z","msg":"借過～容祖兒"},{"pid":"a8d79e41997eed7006af5c2c8876d3a4a005dead","tid":993014,"uid":206244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位 ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa648ba3417f2e19fe743434253fc45cea1aef5c","tid":993014,"uid":94458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:12:36.000Z","msg":"做好準備-何韻詩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}